Taken from [FEEDBACK-14785|https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/FEEDBACK-14785]:

{quote}
The 30 day summary does not handle multiple Versions being released on the same day or within a short time period. The names of the released versions are printed over the top of each other, so you can't read any of them.
I use JIRA when developing reports. I have a component for each report that I build. I create a version when some work is requests on a report. I often release several reports on the same day - hence several versions appear on the 30 day summary in an unreadable format.
{quote}

